    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously preserved to showroom standards. It features a flawless exterior paint finish with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having undergone regular professional maintenance with full documentation provided. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
